Test case #4. Create post

Follow the link https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/
Login data:
Username: Ivan
Password: 123456789123

1. click on the "Create post" button
2. enter the value "Post" in the "Title" field
3. enter the value "Post" in the "Body Content" field
4. select the checkbox "This is a unique post"
5. select "Public" in "Select value"
6. press the button "Save new post" and pay attention to the display on the page



Expected result: post with the title "Post" is displayed on the page


Locators

1. The "Username" field - .//input[@placeholder="Username"]
2. The the "Password" field - .//input[@placeholder="Password"]
3. The "Sign in" button - .//button[text()='Sign In']
4. The "Create post" button - .//a[@href="/create-post"]
5. The "Title" field - .//input[@id="post-title"]
6. The "Body Content" field - .//textarea[@id="post-body"]
7. The checkbox "This is a unique post" - .//input[@id="”UniquePost”"]
8. select "Public" in "Select value" - .//option[text() = 'Общедоступное']
9. The "Save new post" button - .//button[text() = 'Save New Post']
10. post with the title "Post" - .//*[text() = 'Post']
